{"tid":2308486,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「小米」中短期有波動，但整體質素不變","createTime":"2020-12-02T02:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T02:48:26.000Z","uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b598295c01636c10459147e6e8b5c70a4066c4b","tid":2308486,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:30:41.000Z","msg":"小米（1810）擬以先舊後新方式配售10億股，並發行8.55億美元7年期零票息可換股債券，籌資最多40億美元。<br />\n<br />\n相關文件指，配售價介乎每股23.7港元至24.5港元，集資最多245億港元。<br />\n<br />\n第一，反映小米都認為現價貴，是得到資金時機。第二，佢仍想發展，佢話集資所得將用於加強營運資本、擴展業務及進行投資，以增加關鍵領域的市場佔有率及戰略生態系統投資，以及其他一般公司用途。這股長遠仍是正面，不過股價中短期會波動，$20以下較合理。整體質素無變。"},{"pid":"2bafcd0365038101ead36ad2b4c8116f99d53234","tid":2308486,"uid":265628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:44:03.000Z","msg":"如果我有100股 $26買。會變成點？"},{"pid":"8f936ca5894052cd11fb2626682a67ab69949bdf","tid":2308486,"uid":249162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:46:33.000Z","msg":"係，配完都係垃圾一隻，冇得變 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b782e346956b85cd8902fe1c084c4dc63fd2d31","tid":2308486,"uid":169096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bafcd0365038101ead36ad2b4c8116f99d53234","tid":2308486,"uid":265628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:44:03.000Z","msg":"如果我有100股 $26買。會變成點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T02:47:55.000Z","msg":"一年後上40蚊，配股睇長線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f731fc0be796556bcb676f0019350d2e17e8c885","tid":2308486,"uid":265628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b782e346956b85cd8902fe1c084c4dc63fd2d31","tid":2308486,"uid":169096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bafcd0365038101ead36ad2b4c8116f99d53234","tid":2308486,"uid":265628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T